      • ThreadLocalStreamBufferPool

        public ThreadLocalStreamBufferPool​(ByteBufferFactory byteBufferFactory,
                                   int maxThreadLocalPoolSize,
                                   int maxCorePoolSize)

        Instantiate with details of pool sizes.

        The total potential amount of memory used is:

        pooledByteBufferSize * (active buffers + (threadLocalPoolSize * active threads) + corePoolSize).

        Parameters:
        byteBufferFactory - ByteBufferFactory.
        maxThreadLocalPoolSize - Maximum ThreadLocal pool size.
        maxCorePoolSize - Maximum core pool size.
